Title: ❄️✨[ANN][ICO]SINTEZ - Global Digital Economy Platform of Smart Investing❄️✨
Body: New article: SINT price in details  text:  Hello, community! Many peoples write me question - How much price of SINT in ETH ? Here is right answer:  The calculation formula on the ico page is https://sintez.global/ico/  SINT Price: Depends of investment volume divided by fund distribution (price determined by investors)  In short: We do not set the price of the token, at the presale + ico stage, 250 million tokens will be issued in proportion to the amount of funds raised, taking into account the bonuses of each participant. 2 type of bonuses: for the volume and for the time. I.e. the earlier the funds are received and the more they are sent, the greater the proportion of tokens from those who bought them. Thus, investors themselves set the price of the token.  For example when we reach the Second Target on ICO stage = 10000 ETH SINT price will be: 1 ETH ~ 25000 SINT The more invested, the more the price of the token. And bonuses: Early Bonus: pre-sale 100%, from 35 to 25% - target 3000 ETH, 15% - target 10000 ETH Bonus for Volume: ( Volume^0.07 ) –1  for example 5 ETH = 12%, 50 ETH = 31% and so on  When we prepare to ICO stage we create online calculator where you can see you volume of SINT tokens depends of you address, funds and bonuses.

Author: beezle
Title: ❄️✨[ANN][ICO]SINTEZ - Global Digital Economy Platform of Smart Investing❄️✨
Body: I believe the graph you posted applies only to stage 2.  I think the goal for both stages is a total of 13000 ETH:  Stage 1 (pre-sale) of ICO has a goal of 3000 ETH. Stage 2 (main-sale) of ICO has a goal of 10000 ETH.  I think it is merely coincidental that there is a shift at 3000 ETH in the graph.  As to the bonus, one must wonder where the bonus coins come from? Let's take stage 1 as an example.  The ANN states that stage 1 will offer 250mln tokens (COIN) and will end when the goal of 3000 ETH is reached. One must assume all tokens distributed during the stage 1 pre-sale must come from the stated stage 1 supply of 250mln tokens.  Therefore to cover the 100% bonus one must assume that of the 250mln tokens available that only 125mln can be sold. The remaining 125mln tokens are reserved so that they will be used for the 100% pre-sale bonus.  The amount of ETH collected remains the same.  With no pre-sale bonus:        250mln tokens     -------------------- = 83333.33 tokens per ETH (average)           3000 ETH  With 100% pre-sale bonus:        125 mln tokens (sold) + 125 mln tokens (bonus)     ---------------------------------------------------------- = 83333.33 tokens per ETH (average)                                  3000 ETH  The end-result is the same with or without the 100% bonus.  -------------  For the main sale it was a little harder to calculate due to the variable bonus. But fortunately we don't have to worry about the bonus because as we saw above it doesn't affect the end result:      500 mln tokens  ----------------------  =  50000 tokens per ETH (average)        10000 ETH  Final summary based on stated goals and available supply at each sale stage:  Pre-sale: 83333.33  tokens per ETH (average) Main-sale: 50000 tokens per ETH (average)  I specify (average) next to all my results because one must assume that deals will be made with large investors and will ultimately decrease the tokens per ETH for smaller investors, but I would think this is pretty normal. All I know for sure is that if I had 300 ETH or even just 30 ETH to invest you better believe I would negotiate a great price.  Everything I said might be completely wrong as I don't know much about how ICOs operate so please correct me wherever needed.  Thanks! And I think this is a great project, with or without a pre-sale bonus..

Title: ❄️✨[ANN][ICO]SINTEZ - Global Digital Economy Platform of Smart Investing❄️✨
Body: Here is the dev's post about New Year Gifts and how do they plan to manage them  Quote from: RomanSINT on October 28, 2017, 04:48:32 PM Quote from: CryptoBuds on October 28, 2017, 07:26:14 AM Quote from: satrum on October 27, 2017, 08:03:34 PM Quote from: bitcon on October 27, 2017, 07:31:49 PM Interesting idea.  I read some information about ICO. And saw this:  Quote 10% - New Year Bonus (after 2018) Tell me more about it please.   NEW YEAR GIFTS:  Every New Year our strategic investors will receive a New Year gift! The gift will be allocated from a special wallet for gifts to those who hold tokens SINT more than a year. The size of the gift will be proportional to the number of investor tokens. The total volume of gifts is half of the current balance of the wallet. That is, in a year (New Year 2018-2019) investors will receive gifts for 50 million tokens (the payment will take place immediately after the onset of January 1, 2019), after two years (January 1, 2020) - 25 million and so on. Investors who hold tokens from the first stage of the ICO will receive an additional bonus to the gift of 30% (when calculating the distribution ratio). see details about ico on https://sintez.global/ico/  According to the whitepaper, new year gifts is 10% from total issued tokens. Ofc I understand there will be very few long-term investors, but where will you get funds to make new year presents for HODL investors in some years when there will be nothing at this fund?   Every time we take only half of New Year fund. So tokens never end. Their number decreases... BUT the price will grow faster, so it would be very nice gift every year)

Author: satrum
Title: ❄️✨[ANN][ICO]SINTEZ - Global Digital Economy Platform of Smart Investing❄️✨
Body: And we look at it this way: 1. Presale is a greater risk for the investor than the ICO. People always assess risks and possible profits. They can either go to other ICO at the same time and get other bonuses, probably smaller. 2. Similarly, according to our assessment, the more the project develops, the more the early investors will receive. 3. And they, in turn, will be an example for others, since some investors come only when they see that they have already invested.  for example: presale bonus 100% - you can get 1 ETH and take 100% bonus. Such investors can not be much, because they can not greatly affect the price in the total trading volume. ICO bonus begin from 35% * volume bonus. - you can invest early 10 ETH and take 1.35*1.17 ~ 70% bonus or you can invest 50 ETH after invested 10000 ETH from another person - and take ~ 31% bonus These are different types of investors  And we think price will grow: read please BENEFITS OF SINT TOKEN HOLDERS at https://sintez.global/ico/

Author: bitcon
Title: ❄️✨[ANN][ICO]SINTEZ - Global Digital Economy Platform of Smart Investing❄️✨
Body: If I'm correctly understand what founder meant: he talked about second phase of ICO. You cand find answer of it just on this page:  https://sintez.global/ico/  And exactly this:  Quote The other 500 million will be sold in the second stage, which will be held every day until all are sold 500 million. At this stage, tokens are distributed each day in proportion to the invested funds. daily emission following rules: The daily supply volume is calculated as the multiplication of the base volume and two coefficients The basic daily volume is 2 million tokens The first factor is 60 / (60 + number of days from the beginning of the stage). This factor is introduced to smoothly reduce output and prevent sharp price fluctuations after the completion of the second stage The second factor is equal to the logarithm of (1 + X) on the base 2, where X is the ratio of the average emission rates of the token from the previous day to the average price of emission for the previous month. But not less than 0.1 and no more than 10. The first month of the second stage, the coefficient is set equal to 1. The average price is calculated as the ratio of funds raised to the number of issued tokens for a given period. It is introduced to suppress strong fluctuations in the price of the token, and establishes the dependence of the current financing on the success of the team and accordingly their assessment by investors in the form of a price SINT Current daily volume of issue will be published on the site in real time every day.
